description:
There is a tunnel which is under construction. Workers go inside in a sequence
and come out in reverse sequence i.e., person going in will come out last. You have been
given two sequences, IN and OUT. If any worker does not obey the sequence other workers
will be trapped. Determine if all the workers came out safely. 

**Sample Input:**

5

1 2 3 4 5

5 4 3 2 1

**Sample Output:**

1
 
**Constraints:**    
size.sequence_in = n

1 <= n <= 1e5

1 <= sequence_in[i], sequence_out[i] <= 1e9
 
**Note :-**
 
All workers don’t go inside together
title: Tunnel
